## Operators

###  increments

number ++ = number +1

number -- = number -1

### 	boolean 

​	variavel = (false or true)

### 		Ternary

​		string variable= a==b ? "true" : "false"

​		or

​		int variable= a==b ? 1 : 0

### Relational

​			== equal

​			!= diferent

​			>  bigger

​			>= bigger or equal

​			< smaller

​			<= smaller or equal

### 				Logics

​				&&  = "and"

​				|| = "or"



